{"tid":202734,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N套必睇愛情片","createTime":"2017-04-15T17:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T06:07:44.000Z","uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db9252aee89497ffea304e6536ccca68ecf6d8cd","tid":202734,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"The Notebook <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1678oR5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1678oR5.jpg&h=87863d2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTitanic <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/16/010426_10071eb68e88aa32430bc458bb755b47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F010426_10071eb68e88aa32430bc458bb755b47.jpg&h=513d9c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秋天的童話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jy87xCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjy87xCA.jpg&h=c2f7b1be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n500 days of summer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢套睇完唔知點咁 莫名其妙好sad 其實學套戲講呢套係講a story about love 而唔係a love story<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/16/010839_5993ebbadd18679ca83fd1f6c53325e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F010839_5993ebbadd18679ca83fd1f6c53325e8.jpg&h=e9deca95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b209c82216892da08fd42120ec254b0fe4685394","tid":202734,"uid":79469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"500days of summer 睇完個心真係會「那住那住」咁<br />\n佢既故仔冇咩特別 就好似我地普通既愛情咁<br />\n你最愛既人未必係陪到你最後既人<br />\n另外我都推About time<br />\n呢套戲除左愛情之外 仲有親情同人生哲理<br />\n唔介意既可以去睇下"},{"pid":"909e0973479085c9330e4816a6a72336c52359e3","tid":202734,"uid":25496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:28:12.000Z","msg":"Flipped 青澀 睇完呢種會覺得愛情可以好簡直#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#　　Some of us get dipped in flat, some in satin, some in gloss. But every once in a while you find someone who's iridescent, and when you do, nothing will ever compare.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a835be085e2fa214046fbe873cb9d121a34d0cc","tid":202734,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>500days of summer 睇完個心真係會「那住那住」咁<br />\n佢既故仔冇咩特別 就好似我地普通既愛情咁<br />\n你最愛既人未必係陪到你最後既人<br />\n另外我都推About time<br />\n呢套戲除左愛情之外 仲有親情同人生哲理<br />\n唔介意既可以去睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nExactly!!! Summer呢個女仔好有魔力會令你好難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAbout time 都好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRachel McAdams 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 佢套time traveler's wife 都好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d5a8951a90b0075499a9c42042a218893b3062","tid":202734,"uid":15282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:29:13.000Z","msg":"BEGIN AGAIN<br />\nONCE<br />\nABOUT TIME"},{"pid":"b9ed629baae7382704420b5d0579bad8b7fc59f9","tid":202734,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:30:21.000Z","msg":"the theory of everything"},{"pid":"2cd76d77356fda3217e25af8029b0214e1e9a952","tid":202734,"uid":104758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"The curious case of Benjiman Button"},{"pid":"1b1cd65994ba95b3a3354cb031ca40700e30bd66","tid":202734,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"Dear John 幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04